transcripts.text: Greetings all, Paladin here with a quick announcement.  We're going to be hosting a live stream tonight on the White Hats Media Group YouTube channel.  It will be starting around 10.30 p.m.  Eastern Time, 7.30 Pacific.  In our last video, we talked about some of the new things in White Hats world, and one of those new things was Lady Justice would be joining the team and will have her own blog.  on the whitehatsreport.com website.  So she'll be joining me tonight.  We'll be talking about current events and some other things that we feel like are important for the public to know.  So I hope you can join us and welcome Lady Justice to the White Hat team.  Paladin out of here.
